The basic abilities which Summoners possess are:
  - summon:      Gates in a Creature to serve you
  - create:      Makes a Golem to defend you
  - call:        Combines raw Elements for combat
  - brooch:      Communicates with other Summoners
  - drawhp/sp:   Takes hit points or spell points from the Brooch
  - storehp/sp:  Converts hit points or spell points into Brooch power
  - hood:        Blocks out unwanted communication
  - inspect:     Determines whether you can use a weapon or armour
  - state:       Displays your current status
  - silence:     Hides the movements of your Creatures

To see experience needed to gain levels, type: help levels
For more information on any above topic, type: help <topic>
